        {
            "title": "A股收挫  深股跌近2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早段偏軟，深股跌1.85%，創板挫3.4%，兩市成交合計16439.37億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指半日報3913點，跌20點，今早低開18點或0.46%，報3915點， 早段低見3905，跌28點或0.71%，其後跌幅收窄，中段最高見3933，與昨日持平，半日成交7425.01億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指半日跌253點或1.85%，報13471點，今早低開92點或0.67%，報13633點，半日最高報13644，跌81點或0.59%，臨近收市低見13448，挫277點或2.02%，半日成交9014.36億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日報4650點，跌58點或1.25%，今早低開30點或0.64%，報4679點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日報3150點，跌111點或3.4%，今早低開31點或0.95%，報3184點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15332153-a%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e6%8c%ab-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e8%b7%8c%e8%bf%912",
