            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">東京股市半日跌1%，從昨日的紀錄高位回吐。日經指數半日跌492點，報48087點，跌幅1.01%。</p>\n</div>",
